## Fastor CRM Backend (Node.js)

A secure backend system for CRM lead management, built with **Node.js**, **Express**, **SQLite**, **Sequelize**, and **JWT**.  
Handles counselor accounts, lead submission, lead assignment, and role-based access securely.

